data.description: Come see this one before its gone. Popular Sunrise Vistas home with 2 bedroom 2 baths and 2 car garage!  Enjoy community amenities such as 3 pools, basketball cours, parks, dog park all for the low HOA fee of $95.00 per quarter!  This home has an island kitchen with pantry, vaulted ceilings, separate laundry room.  Large rear yard with covered patio plus additional courtyard on side of home. Perfect for investment as its under $200,000.00!!! Home is perfect for a 2nd home. Close to shopping, restaurants and all the conveniences. Fort Mohave, AZ is growing by leaps and bounds. Take this opportunity to own a property where it is all happening.
